install of nixos:

1. boot liveusb
1.1. format disk as in guide
1.2. mount disk
1.3. generate hardware-configuration.nix with "nixos-generate-config --root /mnt"

2. using flakes to install os:
2.1. start nix-shell with 
	"nix-shell -p nixUnstable git"
2.2. clone nixos into /tmp 
	"cd /tmp && git clone https://github.com/marnyg/nixos"
2.3. copy hardware-configuration.nix into cloned repo and add it to git repo
	"cp /mnt/etc/nixos/hard* . && git add ."
2.4. instal the flake with
	"nixos-install --flake .#new"



